<HEADLINE>
FT  04 APR 92 / Finance &amp; The Family Smaller companies slide  - At a glance
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Smaller company indices reflected falls in the stock market this week. The
Hoare Govett Small Companies Index (capital gains version) dropped 2.7 per
cent from 1163.53 on March 26 to 1131.74 on April 2 and the County Smaller
Companies index fell 2.8 per cent from 925.28 to 899.27 over the same
period.
</TEXT>
