<TEXT>
PEUGEOT, the French car maker, has reached agreement with FS Lublin
(formerly Fabryka Samochodow Ciezarowych), a Polish light commercial vehicle
producer, for the small-volume assembly of Peugeot cars in Poland.
Peugeot has signed an industrial co-operation deal with the Lublin-based van
