<TEXT>
SONY (UK), the distributor of Sony electronic products in the UK and
Ireland, yesterday announced plans to relocate its headquarters to a
business park at Weybridge, Surrey, Vanessa Houlder writes.
It has agreed to pay Pounds 29 a sq ft for a 180,000 sq ft building on the
